          </p>
          <br />
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed text-justify">
            <span class="font-semibold">Bahasa Inggris</span> seperti grammar, reading comprehension, vocabulary, dan short essays.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm leading-relaxed text-justify">
